What you need to know:

The 34-year-old Uruguayan scored United's second goal with an excellent diving header in Sunday's come-from-behind victory and had an earlier effort controversially ruled outCavani arrived at Old Trafford as a free agent last October on a deal until the end of the campaign, with the option of a further yearCavani took his tally to eight goals in 29 appearances for the club in a season marred by injuries